#R2DBC: Reactive Relational Database connectivity

特性         |        R2DBC             |      JPA/JDBC
--------------------------------------------------
非同步       |  Yes(Mono/Flux)          |     No(傳統同步)
資料庫連線    | reactive driver(R2DBC)   |    JDBC driver



# Mono vs Flux
Mono<T>: 單一資料 Mono<Book> findById(int id);
Flux<T>: 多筆資料 Flux<Book> findAll();

# POM 要加入MariaDB 才能使用 MySQL

1. @GetMapping("/books")
URL: http://localhost:8080/api/books
GET

2. @PostMapping("/books")
URL: http://localhost:8080/api/books
POST
Body:
{
    "title": "I love Java ",
    "description": "Insert data into database"

}

3. @DeleteMapping("/books")
URL: http://localhost:8080/api/books
DELETE

4. @DeleteMapping("/books/{id}")
URL: http://localhost:8080/api/books/{id}
DELETE